<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Alpha Impresiones 3D</title><link>https://alphacjmav.github.io/calculadora3d/</link><description>Recent content on Alpha Impresiones 3D</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.147.9</generator><language>es</language><atom:link href="https://alphacjmav.github.io/calculadora3d/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Calculadora de Precios</title><link>https://alphacjmav.github.io/calculadora3d/calculadora/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://alphacjmav.github.io/calculadora3d/calculadora/</guid><description>&lt;p>Calculá tus precios de Impresión 3D fácilmente usando la herramienta de Alpha Impresiones:&lt;/p>
&lt;section class="discord-style-section">
&lt;div class="calculator-box">
&lt;div class="spinning-icon">&lt;/div>
&lt;h2>Calculadora de Costos de Impresión 3D&lt;/h2>
&lt;label>Gramos de material usados:
&lt;input type="number" id="gramos" placeholder="Ej: 50">
&lt;/label>
&lt;label>Tiempo de impresión (horas):
&lt;input type="number" id="horas" placeholder="Ej: 3.5">
&lt;/label>
&lt;label>Costo por gramo ($):
&lt;input type="number" id="costoGramo" value="0.25">
&lt;/label>
&lt;label>Costo por hora ($):
&lt;input type="number" id="costoHora" value="150">
&lt;/label>
&lt;button onclick="calcular()">Calcular&lt;/button>
&lt;p id="resultado">&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/section>
&lt;style>
body {
margin: 0;
font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
}
.discord-style-section {
background: linear-gradient(145deg, #4f0599, #1d1b52);
min-height: 100vh;
padding: 3rem 1rem;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
}
.discord-style-section::before {
content: "";
position: absolute;
width: 600px;
height: 600px;
background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
top: -200px;
left: -200px;
border-radius: 50%;
z-index: 0;
animation: float 10s infinite ease-in-out;
}
.calculator-box {
background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #232428, #1c1d20);
border: 2px solid rgba(114, 137, 218, 0.3);
border-radius: 24px;
padding: 2rem;
width: 100%;
max-width: 400px;
box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
position: relative;
z-index: 1;
color: white;
}
.calculator-box h2 {
font-size: 1.7rem;
color: #ffffff;
margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.calculator-box label {
display: block;
margin-bottom: 1rem;
font-size: 0.95rem;
}
.calculator-box input {
width: 100%;
padding: 0.6rem;
margin-top: 0.3rem;
background: #2e3035;
border: 1px solid #444;
border-radius: 8px;
color: #fff;
font-size: 1rem;
}
.calculator-box button {
width: 100%;
margin-top: 1.2rem;
padding: 0.75rem;
background-color: #5865F2;
border: none;
border-radius: 10px;
font-size: 1rem;
font-weight: bold;
color: white;
cursor: pointer;
transition: background 0.3s ease;
}
.calculator-box button:hover {
background-color: #4752c4;
}
#resultado {
margin-top: 1.5rem;
font-size: 1.1rem;
color: #b9bbbe;
text-align: center;
}
@keyframes float {
0% { transform: translateY(0); }
50% { transform: translateY(20px); }
100% { transform: translateY(0); }
}
.spinning-icon {
width: 60px;
height: 60px;
margin: 0 auto 1rem auto;
background-image: url('https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1055/1055646.png');
background-size: cover;
animation: spin 6s linear infinite;
opacity: 0.3;
z-index: 2;
}
@keyframes spin {
0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}
&lt;/style>
&lt;script>
function calcular() {
const gramos = parseFloat(document.getElementById('gramos').value) || 0;
const horas = parseFloat(document.getElementById('horas').value) || 0;
const costoGramo = parseFloat(document.getElementById('costoGramo').value) || 0;
const costoHora = parseFloat(document.getElementById('costoHora').value) || 0;
const total = (gramos * costoGramo) + (horas * costoHora);
document.getElementById('resultado').innerText = `Costo estimado: $${total.toFixed(2)}`;
}
&lt;/script>
